Package: SearchBible
Title: Tools for Accessing Bible Verses from BibleGateway
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Angel", "Feliz", , "angel.esteban.feliz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: |
    This R package provides functions to retrieve Bible verses from BibleGateway.
    The 'find_bible_verse' function allows you to search for Bible verses
    containing specific text, while the 'get_bible_verse' function enables
    retrieval of verses based on their canonical reference (e.g., "John 3:16").
    Both functions support multiple Bible versions and provide formatted output.
